# Superpowers Preferences

When using `superpowers/writing-plans`, save all plans to:

`{{ .chezmoi.homeDir }}/Documents/dev-plans/<repo-name>/plans/YYYY-MM-DD-<feature-name>.md`

This overrides the default project-local plan path.

When using `superpowers/brainstorming`, save all design docs to:

`{{ .chezmoi.homeDir }}/Documents/dev-plans/<repo-name>/specs/YYYY-MM-DD-<feature-name>.md`
